1 the statewide unemployment rate of the Commonwealth:
2 1. In the most recent five (5) consecutive calendar years; or
3 2. By two hundred percent (200%) in the most recent calendar year; and
4 (8) "Kentucky resident" is a Kentucky resident as defined by the council pursuant to
5 KRS 164.020(8).
